reviewText: Really worth it ,affordable price and the figure itself comes with a stand to display

Love this show used to watch it on the weekends. I would say it's appropriate for all ages. Love the fact that it came with a action figure. I ordered 2 copies of this show, one to watch and one to keep inside of a shadow box to have as a collectors item.

This product was a really cool find on Amazon, I have always wanted a Viewtiful Joe figure, and this was it! It does come with a dvd and cool postcard inside, but I got it for the figure which is nice.
